  "Your investments from market losses when considering all relevant disability factors": "",
  "Your vehicle from theft, even when conditions shift significantly": "",
  "Disability insurance protects your greatest asset — your earning capacity. You are statistically more likely to become disabled during your working years than to die, making this coverage critical.": "",
