  "An investment strategy that diversifies across asset classes": "",
  "A method where each person saves individually for potential losses": "",
  "A government program that insures all citizens equally": "",
  "Combining the premiums of many policyholders to fund the claims of the few who experience losses, spreading financial risk": "",
  "Risk pooling is the fundamental concept behind insurance. Large groups of people contribute premiums, creating a fund that pays out claims for the relatively small number who experience covered losses.": "",
